<br>
&quot;You bleed you roll&quot; - If you help in some way to the raid, you have a chance at rolling. <br>
<br>
&quot;Use before profit&quot; - As opposed to need before greed, if you will use it at least some of the time as opposed to selling it for profit, you should roll on it. <br>
